UPDATE: SOLD OUT! THANKS SO MUCH TO EVERYONE WHO BOUGHT A PIECE. MORE SOON!

My first collection of 18 hand-turned, one-of-a-kind, bowls and vases is now up for sale. It’s called Drop One (clever, I know). 10% of all sales of Drop One will be donated to GiveDirectly to help fight poverty. All support is much appreciated. ✌️ 

https://wood-moves.myshopify.com/

I’m really overwhelmed and grateful for the amazing response to Drop One. It sold out in less than 24 hrs! Thank you so much to everyone who bought something. All pieces will be sent out in the next few days. And to everyone who asked about more stock, there will be another collection coming very soon and I will be sure to give notice before the drop this time.

I have happily donated $100 (10% of sales) to GiveDirectly. Swipe to see the donation. 

Thanks again!
✌️ ❤️
